you should become,

13
00:01:13,241 --> 00:01:14,842
and what you could become.

14
00:01:18,546 --> 00:01:22,783
I looked at this place
and saw my unfinished soul.

15
00:01:25,386 --> 00:01:29,790
I looked at this
place and knew, for me...

16
00:01:29,857 --> 00:01:31,425
