a traffic jam too.

129
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:33,240
- Can you help us
ferry folks across?

130
00:09:33,306 --> 00:09:34,507
- I can do that.

131
00:09:34,574 --> 00:09:36,710
- That means
your wife has to drive a wagon.

132
00:09:36,777 --> 00:09:39,713
